Plot: After a near death experience, Gillian returns to her body accompanied by an angel who helped her come back. An invisible guardian that only Gillian can see, he helps her achieve the popularity she has always yearned for. But then, Angel begins to make bizarre demands. At last, Gillian must face the terrifying question: What kind of being has she brought back from the Other Side?
Characters: Ash Redfern, Gillian Lennox, David Blackburn, Gary Fargeon, Amy Nowick, Tanya Jun, Macon Kingsley, Bruce Faber, Cory Zablinski, Kimberlee Cherry, Steffi Lockhart, Daryl Novak, J. Z. Oberlin, Melusine
